title: 686 Picnic Time Mega Can Cooler
description: Extra large (12.25" diameter X 20.75" high) insulated can-replica cooler with pivoting handle and removable lid; 27-can capacity (5-gallon). Can also be used as a seat. Made of HDPE.

transcripts: The Mega Can Cooler by Picnic Time has several things in one. A can, a cooler, and a seat. This extra large insulated cooler looks like your favorite beverage can. It has a pivoting handle and removable lid and can also be used as a seat. Its 27 can capacity ensures that your favorite drink will be cold when you need it. Choose from a variety of full color imprinted designs or customize your own. You can even show your support for your favorite NFL, MBA, MLB or collegiate team. It's perfect for the beach, patio, tailgating, parties, and sporting events. Get one today to make sure your party has enough cold beverages and seats.
